HAPPY NEW YEAR!! 🎉🥳
•
I continue to say that 2022 was a whirlwind of a year. I cannot believe how much I did, the amount of chocolate I made, and how many people I have met. People who has continued to support, follow the journey, and have changed my life 🥹
•
All I have to say is: THANK YOU! Thank you for everything and making my life such a fun and fulfilling one 😭 Here’s to a prosperous 2023 😌 There’s so many people I could tag, can you spot yourself?

🚨🍫 INTRODUCING AURO x @danielcorpuz : CHOCOLATE MASTERCLASS 🍫🚨

In partnership with the iconic Netflix series School of Chocolate Pastry Chef @danielcorpuz , we invite you to a series of chocolate making masterclasses! Learn from the alumni himself as he demonstrates and shares his shares his experience and skills from the show! 

March 10
🍫 Philippine Coffee Bag Demo

Learn how to make one of his iconic pieces from the show during this 5 hour demo.

March 11
🍫 Bonbons and Confections Masterclass

Get your hands dirty and dive into chocolate and learn how to make his beautifully crafted and delicious bonbons first hand to refine and perfect your skills.

Mar 12
🍫 Tinikling Chocolate Sculpture Masterclass

An advance class on chocolate sculpting, learn how to make an impressive edible piece that will surely be a showstopper. 

✨This series of masterclasses is made possible together with @enderuncolleges ! All classes will be hosted in their state-of-the-art culinary amphitheater and kitchens!

‼️ HURRY NOW and head over to our link in bio to secure your slots while they last! LIMITED SLOTS ONLY!

See you in March!

#AuroChocolatexDanielCorpuz #AuroChocolate #Auro #DanielCorpuz #Enderun #Chocolatesculpture #chocolate #cacao

🚨🍫 INTRODUCING AURO x @danielcorpuz NETFLIX’S PHILIPPINE COFFE BAG DEMO 🍫🚨

In collaboration with Netflix's School of Chocolate Pastry Chef @DanielCorpuz and @EnderunColleges, we invite you to a 5-hour demo class wherein you will get to learn from Daniel himself as he skillfully recreates his iconic chocolate Coffee Bag showpiece that was featured on the very first challenge of the show!

This introductory class is perfect for chocolate lovers who want to learn about some of the basic skills needed to create a chocolate showpiece. 

In this demo, you will learn to create and assemble the following components:

✨ Coffee mousse 
✨ Auro Chocolate Cake
✨ Mango Compote
✨ Auro White Chocolate Cremuex

WHEN: MARCH 10, 2023 | 1:00PM TO 6:00PM
WHERE: Culinary Amphitheater, Enderun Colleges

HURRY! Limited slots only! Click the link in our bio to book your slot!
First confirmed paid slots are prioritized.

See you and Daniel there!

#AuroChocolate #AuroxDanielCorpuz #Auro #Enderun #Chocolate #Cacao

It takes two type of people to create the chocolates and confections we are familiar with: farmers who cultivate cacao, and chefs who transform chocolate. 
•
I am so excited to meet both the cacao farmers of @aurochocolate and the pastry chefs and chocolatiers of the Philippines while I’m there in March!
•
•
In collaboration with @aurochocolate
and @EnderunColleges, I will be demonstrating my iconic Philippine Coffee Bag from @netflix ‘School of Chocolate,’ and teaching hands-on Bonbon and Showpiece classes from March 10 - March 12
•
Registration is open now for all three events and there are limited slots! Click the link in our bio to book your slot!
•
And if you’ve ever wanted to try my stuff, I will be doing a pop-up at @aurochocolate’s new store in BGC, Taguig on March 17 and will be there for a meet and greet on March 18! 
•
It’s a full calendar, but I am excited to meet you all in the Philippines!!! 🇵🇭 
•
•
🎞️: @danielcorpuz

As my trip to the Philippines 🇵🇭comes to an end, I just want to say how grateful and thankful I am for every person I have been able to meet in the past 3 weeks!! 😭🥹
•
•
Though my schedule was packed with something planned nearly everyday, I was able to make this trip ‘impactful’ and ‘sulit (worth it)’ which was all I could have asked. Though it was ‘work’ I truly do enjoy what I do and I’m so happy I was able to meet so many people who share that same love for food.
•
•
I will certainly not wait another 15 years to come back, and will be back soon! I’ll definitely be sharing more pics and vids but, I just wanted to say thank you to everyone first! 😭
•
•

You knew him at Netflix’s School of Chocolate. This time, Chef Daniel will showcase his pastry prowess at Half Saints. 

We’ve been working on this collab for months - managing and imagining from New York, Manila, and Tokyo.

Presenting Half Saints x Daniel Corpuz Paris-Brest available in 6 different flavors.

1. Triple Auro Chocolate, Cacao Nibs, Orange
2. Black Sesame, Vanilla, Calamansi
3. Pistachio, Cardamom, Bergamot
4. Espresso, Azuki, Almonds
5. 32% White Chocolate, Cashew, Caramel (Sans Rival)
6. Ube, Banana, 32% White Chocolate

Pre-orders will go live at halfsaints.com this weekend. Pick-up on July 22. Limited slots only.

As always, thank you for choosing HS x DC!
